task.summary: - Fixed bug in Amazon, now can obtain items - Added MP3 preview to osu

- Added more docs - JDAParamParser override #parseParam - Created JDACommandHandler which implements CommandHandler - Fixed bug where message that Command didn't exist is displayed if Module doesn't exist - Fixed bug where couldn't process arrays in param parser - Updated names of fields and variables to be clearer - Implemented Default commands (default command if module is specified but command doesn't exist) - Added more code in the example package (integration test) - Updated JDA
- Deleted BotUtils - Temp bug fix with User (Seems not making aliases lower case) - Set emote get/post as default command in Emote module - Fixed bug in emotes where urls didn't display correctly.
